casebody.data:
Marion WILSON, petitioner,
v.
Eric SELLERS, Warden. No. 16-6855. Supreme Court of the United States March 27, 2017.

In light of the letter filed by respondent on March 15, 2017, the order inviting Adam K. Mortara, Esquire, of Chicago, Illinois, to brief and argue, as amicus curiae, in support of the judgment below is withdrawn.
